Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:16.21,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.97,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:23.93,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.43,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.81,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.94,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.28,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:48.49,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.62,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:03:00.51,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.68,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.47,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.60,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:12.06,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:16.15,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
